1. *Prema* njegovom mišljenju, treba da učinimo sve što je potrebno. (According to his opinion, we should do everything that is necessary.)

2. Ona je još uvek ljuta *prema* njemu. (She is still angry towards him.)

3. On se oseća krivim *prema* njoj. (He feels guilty towards her.)

4. On je bio oštar *prema* njenim idejama. (He was harsh towards her ideas.)

5. Ona je bila poštovana *prema* njemu. (She was respected towards him.)

6. On je bio blag *prema* nama. (He was kind towards us.)